Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.11,0:00:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.77,0:00:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.57,0:00:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.03,0:00:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.61,0:00:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.95,0:00:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.12,0:00:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you just have to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.29,0:00:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words\Nlured men to the Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.00,0:00:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,in pursuit of dreams greater\Nthan they've ever dared
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.17,0:00:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to imagine! This is the time\Nknown as the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.42,0:00:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.01,0:00:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.77,0:00:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.02,0:01:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.74,0:01:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.75,0:01:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.51,0:01:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.51,0:01:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.22,0:01:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.98,0:01:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.65,0:01:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.50,0:02:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.05,0:02:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Say goodbye, swords. Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHuh? Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.39,0:02:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat Burglar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.23,0:02:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,One-Sword Technique's not my\Nforte fellas, but what the hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.40,0:02:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's, go. Butchie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.86,0:02:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Siam! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] If I just had one more\Nsword, I could take these guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] I'm gonna get\Nthe swords back to Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.21,0:02:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NWhat do you need swords for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.38,0:02:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\N"Luffy Back in Action!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kaya's\NDesperate Resistance!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.64,0:03:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.52,0:03:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO] To think that these\Nbrats have held you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How the Black Cat\NPirates have fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO] What have you got\Nto say for yourself? Jango!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO] But... Uh...\NWell... I... You said...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:03:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sorry, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but... you said letting the kid\Ngo wouldn't cause any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO chuckles nervously]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.29,0:04:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NI did say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.25,0:04:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your point?\NHe's an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew no one would\Nlisten to his warnings
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and he would come stumbling back\Nto take a stand against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But the one thing I\Nhadn't taken account for,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,was your inexcusable weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir. We're not weak.\NIt's just that--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[grumbles]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[SIAM]\NWho are you to call us weak?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUTCHIE] Watch what\Nyou say, Captain Kuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[SIAM]\NYou used to be quite the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But, face it, Kuro,\Nit's been three years,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and we haven't exactly\Nbeen living the good life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting on a rich\Ngirl hand and foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUTCHIE chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,For three long years, we've\Nbeen out sinking pirate ships
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and massacring villages!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good. Finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You've done nothing this\Nwhole time! We've been killing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.59,0:04:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You butler! There's no way you\Ncan beat the Meowban Brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't! Butchie, Siam, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUTCHIE, SIAM yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[SIAM]\NYou are not our captain anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[SIAM laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUTCHIE] So sorry,\Nbut we have to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What? He's behind 'em?\NHow the hell'd he--?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And what're those crazy weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO] Who? Who are\Nyou going to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUTCHIE, SIAM yelp]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.15,0:05:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He snuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Right behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:05:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[SIAM]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUTCHIE]\NAh! He-He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.53,0:06:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.83,0:06:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NThe... Pussyfoot Maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NPussyfoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUTCHIE, SIAM whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NYou know, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUTCHIE, SIAM whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I do feel... a bit sluggish\Nafter all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHe's handling them like babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And, those two\Nnearly defeated Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NWith his Pussyfoot Maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.57,0:06:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Kuro could shred\Neveryone on this beach
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,before we drew our next breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.99,0:06:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't even see it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no escape from a\Nkilling machine like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew he hadn't grown soft when\NI saw that old habit of his,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.59,0:06:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that strange way of\Nlifting his glasses
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.71,0:06:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,so that he won't cut his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like he never stopped\Nwearing those cat claws.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.55,0:07:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They're almost\Na part of his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, he hasn't\Nforgotten how to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.81,0:07:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,0:07:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very lucky.\NI'm feeling somewhat merciful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe these years on dry\Nland have made me soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NI'll give you five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.26,0:07:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO] If you can't\Ndeal with the situation here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in five minutes, then I'll\Nkill every last one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.02,0:07:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, have I made myself clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs nervously]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course,\Nthat's perfectly clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.03,0:08:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being\Nso forgiving!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have to do is\Ntake care of this one guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Five minutes will be more\Nthan enough time for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO laughs nervously]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUTCHIE] We nearly had\Nhim a few minutes ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[SIAM] We won't need one\Nminute to finish him this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you!\NKill him! Kill him, dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,--[footsteps]\N--[JANGO] Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Easy there! You can't just\Nkick 'em! Those're my swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.57,0:08:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How 'bout a "thanks"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.24,0:08:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha. I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[SIAM] You idiot! It won't\Nmatter how many swords you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:09:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUTCHIE] Now you'll die\Nholding three of 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NTiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You still... don't... get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The clock is ticking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Carrying three swords\Nwon't help you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.69,0:09:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless, you know\NThree-Swords Style.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO] He took down the Meowban\NBrothers with one attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.15,0:10:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.28,0:10:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NDon't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can promise you. Everything\Nwill be taken care of...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...in less than five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.33,0:10:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Three. Three minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUTCHIE groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.02,0:10:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUTCHIE]\NI'll... I'll slaughter him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUTCHIE coughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do it... Hypnotize me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.53,0:10:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUTCHIE coughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Just... do it... Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.99,0:10:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still alive.\NYou do sloppy work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.41,0:10:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,0:11:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So he is. I guess all that\Nblubber protected his vitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Butchie! Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Really?\NYou back for more?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.99,0:11:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NThis guy means business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.29,0:11:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He was trouble when\Nhe was half this size.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Then Jango had to\Nflip his psycho switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.64,0:11:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NNow's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta wake that lazy\Njerk up while I still can!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.23,0:12:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NWhat is that girl up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.81,0:12:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NSomething tricky I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] Everyone else is\Nbusy fighting for their lives
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.07,0:12:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's just sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up! You bum!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.92,0:12:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami! Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.59,0:12:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Two minutes. And counting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up! You bum!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami! Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO chuckles]\NIt was nice knowing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.21,0:13:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dodge it! Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.38,0:13:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] I thought it was\Njust a hypnotic charm,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's also his weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami! You can not just go around\Nstepping on people's eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No! How is that\Ntwerp still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's either the best timing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.28,0:13:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,or the worst timing in\Nthe world. I can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFy grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.22,0:13:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Owww!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.89,0:14:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! That guy's\Nback in the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No! This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.23,0:14:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Five minutes'll\Nnever be enough time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.61,0:14:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh! That hurts, you jerk!\NWhy'd you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, sleeping beauty,\Nthat wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't... me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay? Nami, did you\Nget hurt? Let me see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NOh, it's nothing. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done everything\NI can for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.84,0:14:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, we have to win. We can't\Nafford to lose this fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.68,0:14:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it... for the treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.31,0:14:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, all right. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.98,0:14:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Go. Win this and\Nprotect my treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Yeah, yeah,\Nthe treasure, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,One minute. And counting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't possibly finish\Nthem in one minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, guys, stop messing\Naround and end this already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.47,0:15:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Butchie! Quickly! There's\Nno more time to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill that three sword bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of the\Nfreaky, bendable kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NI'm coming for you, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph. Times up.\NYou knew the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.33,0:15:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.43,0:16:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Hey, wait. Why is\Nthat shady butler here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.02,0:16:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that kid. Didn't\Nhe die falling off a cliff?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.23,0:16:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.04,0:16:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ever sneak up on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NUnless you want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Ussop. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NKaya... what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.28,0:17:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Usopp. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.41,0:17:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how\Nyou'll ever forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...that Klahadore is a\Nscheming, murdering pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NNevermind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya, your life is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.71,0:17:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to run\Nsomewhere safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.51,0:17:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't! You're still here\Nfighting! I won't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You fought for me after\NI treated you so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at you,\Nyou're barely alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.06,0:17:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're still so brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I just--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NThis is no place for a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam, please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. Stop. Don't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.87,0:17:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop this right\Nnow, Klahadore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.79,0:18:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you're up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry already told me\Nabout everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.59,0:18:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO] Hm? What's the girl from\Nthe mansion doing down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole reason\Nthat we're here
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,is to murder that\Nlittle rich girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.43,0:18:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE G]\NIf she's here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.27,0:18:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,then we don't have\Nto go to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE I] All we gotta\Ndo is kill her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NKlahadore, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.90,0:18:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want my fortune,\Nyou can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it all and leave\Nthis village right now
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO] I will gladly accept\Nyour fortune, Miss Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.58,0:18:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, simply acquiring\Nwealth isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.71,0:18:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,More than anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.63,0:18:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What I want... is peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You want peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.64,0:18:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Just peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace of mind.\NIt's simple really.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.39,0:18:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I have spent the\Nlast three years
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,earning the trust of\Nthe entire village,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and, to be honest,\NI find this new sense
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.65,0:19:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,of peace and tranquility\Nquite comforting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.57,0:19:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,When my plan comes to fruition,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I will live with this\Nsublime peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.33,0:19:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The glorious comfort\Nof a peaceful life
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.34,0:19:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,will be mine for\Nforever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In short, these\Npirates are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And you... will leave your\Nfortune to me and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kaya, these\Nthings will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You just can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away, Kaya! There's\Nno use talking to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NYou're not Klahadore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.24,0:20:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave here, right now!\NNever come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NOh, you'd point a gun at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Just leave! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I see. You're\Nall grown up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So much has happened\Nin the last three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember the\Nthings we went through?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.98,0:20:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We spent so much time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.65,0:20:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Even before your dear sweet\Nparents passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You were more than my master,\Nyou were my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.58,0:20:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So many memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Together we suffered and\Ntogether we rejoiced.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.30,0:20:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Like family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.17,0:20:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Klahadore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.93,0:20:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO] I took you on\Nshopping trips to the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.51,0:21:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked after you so\Ndiligently when you were ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And we used to talk\Nfor hours and hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.44,0:21:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya, listen to me.\NI was devoted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,For so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.65,0:21:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,For so very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I endured it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.12,0:21:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I quietly suffered so that\Ntoday I could end your life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and take everything\Nthat I deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I, who was once the feared\Nand respected Captain Kuro,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,had to bow and humble myself
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.39,0:21:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,before some snot-nosed\Nlittle girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It went against every\Nfiber of my being.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:21:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:22:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO] Can you understand the\Ndepth of these daily insults?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.41,0:22:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you understand the rage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.20,0:22:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,created by those transgressions\Nagainst my pride?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.71,0:22:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NKuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.30,0:22:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for reminding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.72,0:22:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp, I owe you for hitting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.89,0:22:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get even.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.52,0:22:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.56,0:22:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If I recall, you hit me as\Nhard as you could, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.61,0:22:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.11,0:22:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.57,0:22:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.43,0:23:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] If he hates\Ngetting hit that much,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.60,0:23:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,he's about to have\Na really bad day!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.27,0:23:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.65,0:23:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.27,0:23:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.03,0:23:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.16,0:23:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.87,0:23:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.37,0:23:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.09,0:23:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.01,0:23:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.64,0:23:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.94,0:23:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.78,0:24:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.82,0:24:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.78,0:24:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.04,0:24:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.91,0:24:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.47,0:24:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NUsopp! Go save Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.47,0:24:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the butler to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.80,0:24:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] That guy can't\Nhelp but to be evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.81,0:24:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Too bad.\NI had something else in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.23,0:24:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] I'm going\Nafter that hypno freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.52,0:24:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Kuro! You're not\Ncut out for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.77,0:24:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you what a real\Npirate looks like!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.73,0:24:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.69,0:24:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Beat Kuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.74,0:24:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp the Man's\NTearful Resolve!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.24,0:24:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates!

